usage: ped OPTIONS [file...]
       ped --help
       ped --version

  The pedestrian text editor.

  OPTIONS
    --show-spotlight
        Highlights the cursor row.

    --show-lines
        Show line numbers in the left margin.

    --show-eol
        Show the end-of-line as a special character.

    --config FILE
        Load configuration from FILE instead of searching in default locations.
